### Sign Out [POST]

**This end-point was not supplied in the original CodeCafé document, but is required.**

This resource has the user's id as a parameter, and will delete the current user session and sign the user out of the platform.

The login token will expire.

It should return 200 if a user session exists, 401 otherwise.

+ Response 200 (application/hal+json)

    ```
